# 360World is a Bring-Your-Own-Key app: no server-side secrets are required.
# This file exists as a placeholder. Users provide their OpenAI or Replicate
# API key directly in the UI; it is stored locally in the browser's IndexedDB
# and only ever sent client-side — directly to api.openai.com for OpenAI, or
# via the Authorization header to the CORS proxy for Replicate.
